## ğŸ›¡ï¸ Project Overview

ZauriScoreâ„¢ is an advanced AI-powered smart contract security analysis platform that combines machine learning with traditional security analysis techniques to provide comprehensive vulnerability detection and risk assessment for Ethereum smart contracts.

## ğŸ› ï¸ Key Features

### ğŸ” Multi-layered Security Analysis
- Static Analysis (Slither)
- Pattern Matching
- ML-based Vulnerability Detection
- Gas Optimization Checks

### ğŸ¤– AI-Powered Analysis
- CodeBERT Model Integration
- Vulnerability Pattern Learning
- Risk Score Prediction
- Code Similarity Analysis

### ğŸ“Š Comprehensive Reporting
- Vulnerability Details
- Risk Scoring
- Remediation Suggestions
- Gas Optimization Tips

